onChildTerminated

protected boolean onChildTerminated(org.smartfrog.sfcore.prim.TerminationRecord record,
                                    org.smartfrog.sfcore.prim.Prim comp)
Handle child termination. Sequence behaviour for a normal child termination is
  1. to start the next component.
  2. if it is the last - terminate normally.
  3. If starting the next component raised an error, terminate abnormally
Abnormal child terminations are relayed up.

Overrides:
onChildTerminated in class org.smartfrog.sfcore.workflow.eventbus.EventCompoundImpl
Parameters:
record - exit record of the component
comp - child component that is terminating
Returns:
true whenever a child component is not started
